Package: econioread
Type: Package
Title: Read Input-Output Tables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mizuki", "Uchida", , "uchidamizuki@vivaldi.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a step-by-step interface for reading input-output
    tables from 'csv', 'xls', and 'xlsx' files into 'econio' input-output
    table objects. Handles the extraction of headers, regions, sector
    names, and sector types from raw spreadsheet cells, supporting both
    regional and multiregional input-output tables.
